dev pipeline (continuous running process)
   our code -> webpack -> webpack dev server -> addr: localhost:8080

production pipeline (heroku as an example)
   our code -> push to heroku -> install npm modules -> run 'postinstall' -> run 'start' -> addr: xyz.herkuapp.com

   package.json named scripts
     postinstall exmaple: npm run postinstall
                 ran immediately asfter installing npm modules

     start       example npm run start
                 responsible for starting and maintaining the server